# Local Pages Functions: copy this file to `.dev.vars` (do not commit real secrets)
# and run from the project root, for example:
#   npx wrangler pages dev . --kv schedules_kv
# Use your real KV namespace id in wrangler / dashboard bindings.
#
# Required for bearer tokens, roster scoping, and supervision invites:
TIMETABLE_AUTH_SECRET=replace-with-a-long-random-string
#
# Optional — reject unauthenticated API access in production-like mode:
# TIMETABLE_REQUIRE_AUTH=1
